  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Auditing for UK auditors and audit firms operating in the EEA after Brexit
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">What UK audit firms, UK auditors, and those with UK audit qualifications need to do.</p>

  </div>
</div>

